# Changelog

All notable changes to VP SEO are documented here.
This project adheres to [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/) and
[Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

## [1.0.2] — 2026-06-19

### Fixed
- `og:description` and `twitter:description` now use the same ~160-character
  description as the `<meta name="description">` tag, instead of generating a
  separate, longer (~200-char) version from the article text. Social previews are
  no longer flagged as over-long by validators.

## [1.0.1] — 2026-06-18

### Changed
- Update server path standardised to `update.xml`.

### Added
- Changelog is now shown in Joomla's update view (via `changelogurl`).

## [1.0.0] — 2026-06-17

Initial public release.

### Added
- **SEO Title** field per article — browser title separate from the H1 (Publishing tab).
- **OpenGraph** tags: `og:title`, `og:description`, `og:type`, `og:url`,
  `og:site_name`, `og:locale`, `og:image`.
- **Twitter Card** tags: `twitter:card`, `twitter:title`, `twitter:description`, `twitter:image`.
- **Automatic meta description** generated from article content when none is set,
  trimmed to a search-friendly length.
- **SVG-safe social images** with a configurable default-image fallback.
- `article:published_time` and `article:modified_time`.
- Honours Joomla's global "Include Site Name in Page Titles" setting.

> The Pro edition adds title templates, per-article social overrides, canonical
> management, `article:author`/`section`/`tag`, `og:image` dimensions/type/alt, and a
> live social-card preview in the editor.

